Comment: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.66,Lyrics kanji,,0,0,0,,こだまが胸に はずんでくるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.66,Lyrics romaji,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:15.03,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,The chest trembles in blissful ease,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:20.66,Lyrics eng,,0,0,0,,echoing with mountain peaks
